        <article id="details-article" class="col-sm-8">
            <h1 id="article-title">Your Product <span class="font-weight-light">Product Name</span></h1>
           

            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, in nam feugiat eleifend. Sea an possit offendit definiebas, usu cu aeque mediocritatem. Vis constituam suscipiantur ad, cum duis concludaturque no. Sea vocent consulatu at.</p>

